desc: Nut King is a one-stop online store that provides premium quality dry fruits online. We provide medjool dates, roasted pistachios, organic honey, and more.

layout.text: Welcome to Nut King Online Store

We are a family owned and run business since 1983. Under our fathers’ previous name, Star Products Inc, we continue to strive for the best quality goods. We have been around nuts our entire life and only deliver the best quality. We continue to grow and develop with a bigger network online from producer to consumer directly. We are looking to change the status quo in the produce industry.
